rta.activation classes alongside the API artifact; tests should still validate behavior relevant to jakarta.activation-api and avoid broad implementation-only assertions.\",\n    \"The original compile failure is primarily a package migration issue from javax.activation to jakarta.activation; the extra dependency does not replace that source update.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_096fd3ed02a6f215016a40d3603f808193821536001851c59f\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1508, "output": 826, "cacheRead": 25600, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 27934, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782633302927, "responseId": "resp_096fd3ed02a6f215016a40d358277c8193b6f14d767e6d3fa9"}}
